lead_paragraph: With his "headteacher" aura and astute offseason recruitment, Ronald Koeman is making an immediate impact at Everton and getting the best out of the club's strongest squad in a generation.

headline.print_headline: Everton Dreaming Again After Fast Start Under Koeman
